It&apos;s only the beginning of September, but we&apos;re already getting some autumn colors. Sogenchi Pond at Tenryuji Temple.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
まだ9月に入ったばかりですが、もう紅葉が始まっていますね。天龍寺の曹源池にて。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Tenryu-ji" /><summary type="html">It&apos;s only the beginning of September, but we&apos;re already getting some autumn colors. Sogenchi Pond at Tenryuji Temple.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2209_A7R02060.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2209_A7R02060.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kishin Kissa・喜心喫茶</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220902/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kishin Kissa・喜心喫茶" /><published>2022-09-02T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-09-02T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kisshin</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220902/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
