  Kyoto Tower and Karasuma Street at dusk, with rain clouds behind.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
 京都タワーと烏丸通り、夕暮れ時、後ろに雨雲がある。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Clouds" /><category term="Kyoto Tower" /><summary type="html">Kyoto Tower and Karasuma Street at dusk, with rain clouds behind.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2209_A7R02045.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2209_A7R02045.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Evening in Arashiyama・嵐山の夕暮れ</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220831/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Evening in Arashiyama・嵐山の夕暮れ" /><published>2022-08-31T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-08-31T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/togetsukyo</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220831/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  Long exposure blurs the lights and water, at the Togetsu Bridge.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
 長時間露光で光と水をぼかす、渡月橋にて。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><summary type="html">Long exposure blurs the lights and water, at the Togetsu Bridge.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2208_A7R02016.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2208_A7R02016.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">3 Views of Tokyo・東京三景</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220830/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="3 Views of Tokyo・東京三景" /><published>2022-08-30T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-08-30T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/tokyo</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220830/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  Some photos of rainy Tokyo today. First is the Nino Torii at Meiji Jingu. Below left, Nishi Shinjuku from above Shinjuku station, including the Cocoon Tower of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mode.ac.jp/english&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Tokyo Mode Gakuen&lt;/a&gt;. Below right, Tokyo Station with a view of the &lt;a href=&quot;/190607/&quot;&gt;Marunouchi Station building&lt;/a&gt; and surrounding downtown skyscrapers; and Yamanote, Tokaido and Shinkansen trains.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
今日の雨の東京の写真をいくつか。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    まず、明治神宮の二の鳥居。左下は、新宿駅上からの西新宿。&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mode.ac.jp/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;東京モード学園&lt;/a&gt;のコクーンタワーも見える。右下は東京駅で、&lt;a href=&quot;/190607/&quot;&gt;丸の内駅舎&lt;/a&gt;と周囲の都心の高層ビル群、そして山手線、東海道本線、東海道新幹線が見える。
&lt;/p&gt;
  
