 &lt;/div&gt;   
 &lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Torii" /><category term="Architecture" /><category term="Trains" /><summary type="html">Some photos of rainy Tokyo today. First is the Nino Torii at Meiji Jingu. Below left, Nishi Shinjuku from above Shinjuku station, including the Cocoon Tower of Tokyo Mode Gakuen. Below right, Tokyo Station with a view of the Marunouchi Station building and surrounding downtown skyscrapers; and Yamanote, Tokaido and Shinkansen trains.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2208_A7R01996.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2208_A7R01996.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Danish &amp;amp; Espresso</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220828/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Danish &amp;amp; Espresso" /><published>2022-08-28T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-08-28T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/danish</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220828/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
