Looking south at Meiji Jingu and the Shibuya skyline from Shinjuku; the opposite view from &lt;a href=&quot;/211117/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;this photo from last year&lt;/a&gt;.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
明治神宮と渋谷を南から見る。&lt;a href=&quot;/211117/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;昨年の写真&lt;/a&gt;では反対側の景色。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Views" /><category term="Skylines" /><summary type="html">Looking south at Meiji Jingu and the Shibuya skyline from Shinjuku; the opposite view from this photo from last year.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2208_A7R01945.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2208_A7R01945.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Zushi Marina・逗子マリナ</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220826/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Zushi Marina・逗子マリナ" /><published>2022-08-26T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-08-26T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/zushi-marina</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220826/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Pink clouds at dusk, at the Shonan Zushi Marina.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
夕暮れ時のピンクの雲、湘南の逗子マリーナにて。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Boats" /><summary type="html">Pink clouds at dusk, at the Shonan Zushi Marina.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2208_A7R01888-Pano.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2208_A7R01888-Pano.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Onari Street・御成通り</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220825/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Onari Street・御成通り" /><published>2022-08-25T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-08-25T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/onari-st</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220825/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Dusk street scene in the picturesque beach town of Kamakura, south of Tokyo.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
東京の南に位置する風光明媚な海辺の町、鎌倉の夕暮れ時の街並み。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Dusk" /><summary type="html">Dusk street scene in the picturesque beach town of Kamakura, south of Tokyo.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2208_A7R01720.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2208_A7R01720.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Summer on The Strand</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220821/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Summer on The Strand" /><published>2022-08-21T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-08-21T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/summer-strand</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220821/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Beautiful afternoon for spending time on the beach.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;ストランドの夏&lt;/div&gt;
ビーチで過ごすのに最適な午後。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Manhattan Beach" /><category term="Strand" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Piers" /><summary type="html">Beautiful afternoon for spending time on the beach.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2208_A7R01675-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2208_A7R01675-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>